(If you don't receive an answer after approx. 2-3 weeks, please try once
more, because it is possible that a mail disappears or I forgot to answer
your mail.)
@endnode

@node WWW Page
@title "WWW Page"


@{b}@{u}FLM in Internet@{ub}@{uu}

In Internet you can find also a FLM page under @{b}http://dictionary.notrix.de@{ub}.
On this pages are the newest informations about FLM (Amiga + Java + Windows 3.1, NT, 95).

Moreover from here you can download the most recent version of FLM and the
last beta version.
Also there are @{b}all@{ub} available dictionaries for FLM.

@endnode

@node Updates
@title "Updates"

@{b}@{u}Updates@{ub}@{uu}

As a new version is ready, I'll inform you in writing.
Minor updates will be free of charge, and you can find them in the @{" WWW Page " link WWW Page}
of FLM. Moreover, new versions are regularly loaded on Aminet.

See also @{" FLM Support " link FLM_Support}.
@endnode

@node Future Developments
@title "Future Developments"

@{b}@{u}Future Developments@{ub}@{uu}

Planned are:
- a encyclopedia function
- further ARexx commands
- ...

If you should have additional improvement possibilities, I would be very
grateful if you send me them.

Furthermore, in future, should be@{b} @{ub}considered the grammar in translation.
@endnode

